Ellie Bamber https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellie_Bamber 0 Eleanor Elizabeth "Ellie" Bamber (born 2 February 1997) is an English actress. In 2018, she won third prize at the Ian Charleson Awards for her 2017 performance as Hilde in The Lady from the Sea at the Donmar Warehouse.
